n本週三，中國地震台網通報青海玉樹縣墜落一顆類似隕石的物體，其他細節不詳。<br />\n<br />\n數理副博士、俄羅斯車里雅賓斯克國立在學理論物理系副教授扎莫茲德拉稱：「這是一顆超級隕石，發光時間非常久，約29秒。它幾乎是沿切線進入地球的：它的軌跡與水平線的夾角小於10度。」<br />\n<br />\n2013年2月15日，車里雅賓斯克州數千人發現空中出現一顆非常明亮的火流星。這顆隕石在飛行的前幾分鐘膨脹並黑煙環燒，之後遭遇氣浪，發出巨裂爆炸的聲響。隕石碎片墜入切巴爾庫爾市附近，最大的一塊超過600公斤，發現於切巴爾庫爾湖。<br />\n<br />\n目前，隕石碎片被放置在車里雅賓斯克國家歷史博物館展廳，觀眾可進入參觀。博物館的流星碎片重約500公斤。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T03:49:49.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">2013，2015<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"98fccc01d2a436ecf46cb76ee5050315ca25238e","tid":2340933,"uid":60423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T03:55:20.000Z","msg":"Wfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />習大大都未care啲賤民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f1979f24ee5b4141b146dfe7354f2675eea61c3","tid":2340933,"uid":114023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b13657fb3a004f8eb4ac5d913cff00cd6179ba49","tid":2340933,"uid":55458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T03:03:51.000Z","msg":"正文之君<br />\n受命於天"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T03:57:44.000Z","msg":"羽白之君<br />\n受命於天"},{"pid":"118971092bafbc6a89967425a978da70f02a0575","tid":2340933,"uid":80561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f2b6f91c651a1b23f4213588499cadc781f8895","tid":2340933,"uid":143016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T02:55:34.000Z","msg":"執到 係咪就發達？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T04:00:37.000Z","msg":"封到啲中國人已經煮黎食咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4371d5acdf4e9069db85dd3cb02d8687396bb263","tid":2340933,"uid":383204,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9cf5b99e77992ebab7606656e695d88c8714efef","tid":2340933,"uid":57677,"like":6,"dislike":51,"score":-45,"quote":{"pid":"ccde25b557e87ba93b2eae41e91d0c4887b11833","tid":2340933,"uid":284432,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":